Shaun Ingram booked his Ford Focus ST in for a major service and MOT .
But when he went to collect his car, he was shocked to discover mechanic had taken it for a spin at 57mph in a 30mph zone .
Mr Ingram, from Saltash in Cornwall, says it was a pre-planned thing, not spur of the moment .
He said: 'I was left open-mouthed. The mechanic was abusing my trust'